  "title": "Associate Relationship Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job ID: 1059795</strong></p><p>Are you a motivated self-starter who enjoys working with people and is curious about building a career in <strong>banking and wealth management</strong>?</p><p>This role is ideal for <strong>non-experienced candidates or career switchers</strong> who want hands-on exposure to Relationship Management, client advisory, and financial solutions — with structured training and on-the-job support.</p><h3><strong>What You’ll Be Doing</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Learn to conduct <strong>consultative financial discussions</strong> with clients to understand their goals and needs</p></li><li><p>Support the recommendation of suitable banking, investment, and wealth solutions under guidance</p></li><li><p>Build and nurture <strong>long-term client relationships</strong> through regular engagement and follow-ups</p></li><li><p>Share relevant market insights, product updates, and basic financial concepts with clients</p></li><li><p>Gain exposure to a broad range of financial solutions, including:</p><ul><li><p>Savings and banking products</p></li><li><p>Investments and unit trusts</p></li><li><p>Bancassurance and protection solutions</p></li><li><p>Loans and basic financing products</p></li></ul></li><li><p>Participate in branch initiatives, campaigns, and business development activities</p></li><li><p>Develop core skills in <strong>communication, relationship management, and client advisory</strong></p></li></ul><h3><strong>What We’re Looking For</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Local Diploma or Degree in any discipline</p></li><li><p>Strong interest in sales, relationship management, or financial advisory</p></li><li><p>Positive attitude, resilience, and willingness to learn</p></li><li><p>Comfortable speaking with clients and building rapport</p></li><li><p>Self-motivated, goal-driven, and open to feedback and coaching</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Why This Role</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Entry-level opportunity to <strong>start a Relationship Manager career</strong></p></li><li><p>Structured training and mentorship provided</p></li><li><p>Exposure to real client interactions and wealth management products</p></li><li><p>Clear career progression </p></li><li><p>Ideal for candidates exploring a <strong>long-term career in banking</strong></p></li></ul><p><em>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified. However, all applications will be retained in our resume bank for future opportunities.</em><br />Privacy Policy: <a href=\"https://goodjobcreations.com.sg/en/privacy-policy/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://goodjobcreations.com.sg/en/privacy-policy/</a></p><p><strong>EA Personnel Name:</strong> Gabriel Tan<br /><strong>EA Personnel Reg. No.:</strong> R22104076<br /><strong>EA Licence No.:</strong> 07C5771</p>",
